## Steps to run this project

1. python -m venv .venv (if needed)
2. activate the venv (use the correct command for your shell)

Cmd
- run in project root
.venv\Scripts\activate.bat

Powershell
- run in project root
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

- if blocked by execution policy (run once as admin or set for current user)
Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser

Git Bash
- run in project root â€” you must source it so the current shell is modified
source .venv/Scripts/activate
- or
. .venv/Scripts/activate

3. pip install -e .
4. uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 3005